skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
You now have the latest news & information from around the world of handball, courtesy of WPHLiveTV. Up-to-date tournament scores, post match recaps and previews-- all updated throughout the week.

Just add WPHLiveTV Handball News to your Flash Briefing, then say "Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?" to tune in.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
